Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.92,0:00:03.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as flowing water has no form,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.83,0:00:05.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the breeze is invisible,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.39,0:00:06.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,deductions take all shapes & styles in each and every case to be solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.86,0:00:08.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one knows what will happen with this couple nor the outcome of this crime
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.73,0:00:10.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Words are not necessary for feelings are conveyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.70,0:00:12.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sees through the one and only truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.47,0:00:14.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child in appearance with the I.Q. of an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.17,0:00:16.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,no case is left unsolved with Detective Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.43,0:01:43.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While exploring a limestone cave
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.06,0:01:45.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am shot by a gang of bank robbers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.53,0:01:48.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a blood transfusion from Ran saves my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.70,0:01:53.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have made up my mind to tell Ran everything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:01:57.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Ai points a gun at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:01.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then, on the day of\NTeitan High School's school fest,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.38,0:02:06.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,during the play in the gymnasium a murder takes place in the audience!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.59,0:02:13.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai mixes up a potion that restores me to my old body
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.63,0:02:15.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I solve the case immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:18.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thankfully, Ran's suspicions are dispelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:22.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The next day, I ask Ran
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:26.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to have dinner with me at the roof top restaurant in the Beika Center Building
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.04,0:02:30.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but once again,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.38,0:02:31.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we are caught up in another murder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.65,0:02:36.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I leave Ran waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:37.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,as I go off to investigate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.65,0:02:39.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I quickly deduce who the killer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:47.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was right, he killed Mr.\NTatsumi after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.93,0:02:50.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it was Mr. Oba, no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:59.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,PERILOUS RETURN-PLACE WHERE\NVOWS ARE MADE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:09.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:12.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,what does Shinichi want to tell me... what could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:16.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A proposal, he's going to propose!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.39,0:03:18.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.19,0:03:20.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it, it can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:25.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean, we're still in high school...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:28.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sigh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:32.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wish Shinichi'd hurry and come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.18,0:03:41.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...I'm absolutely sure Mr. Oba shot Mr. Tatsumi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:44.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I have two unanswered questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:48.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't explain the strange actions\NMr. Tatsumi took in the elevator, and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.42,0:03:50.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the lack of powder burns...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:55.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,seeing how confident he acted, I'm sure he did something so we wouldn't find any
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.59,0:03:57.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,powder burns on him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:04:01.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know, maybe that's how he did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:04.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Oba was wearing an animal costume at the party, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:06.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:08.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He could have changed his clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.61,0:04:10.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:12.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.91,0:04:15.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,tonight's party was in part, to celebrate
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:17.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the unveiling of our new company mascot,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:20.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the character was on stage all night
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:24.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were shocked when we found out\NMr. Oba was inside it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:25.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We really were...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:26.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:30.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so if he had another set of the same outfit,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:32.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he could have switched it with the one with the powder burns on them...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:35.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he couldn't have!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:40.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before he changed into his costume,\NMr. Oba handed us his jacket & slacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.14,0:04:42.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:43.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is suspicious, isn't he...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.14,0:04:45.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't talk like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.94,0:04:48.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He worked really hard to make us laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:51.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about that character winking?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:53.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, it was funny at first...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:57.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but that's the only thing he did, after a while, it got pretty stale...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.72,0:04:58.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.22,0:05:01.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind, may I take a look at that costume?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.23,0:05:05.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Why am I perspiring so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:07.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The design's very surreal, isn't it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.27,0:05:09.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it adorable?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:11.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who was in charge of the party?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.94,0:05:12.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Oba!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.51,0:05:19.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got it... so that's how he did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.68,0:05:22.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So did you figure it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:23.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, most of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.45,0:05:28.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it getting hot in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:32.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must be kidding! It's freezing, the cooler's on so high...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:34.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Why am I perspiring so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:47.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ugh... this... can't ... be... happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.87,0:05:49.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.11,0:05:52.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,no, not now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.51,0:05:54.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.05,0:05:58.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,not on this important day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:00.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,darn it all...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:02.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:03.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:05.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:10.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure! We found no traces of powder on Mr. Oba!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:12.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:15.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then was it a hold up after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:17.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright then, let's ask around if anyone suspicious was seen going in
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:19.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or out this building while the party was in progress!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:22.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:24.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there's no need for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:25.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:27.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer is already among us...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:33.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, shall we step up to the stage, where the truth awaits us...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:37.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:39.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You already checked me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:42.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They didn't find anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:46.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So why're you treating me like i'm the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:49.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, just calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:52.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You tell them.\NTell them I couldn't have done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.57,0:06:55.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll swear to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:59.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Oba was with me the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:03.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naturally, I wasn't with him when he changed into his costume,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:04.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but the dressing room was locked...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:07.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,besides, there were other people with him so he couldn't have
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:10.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,slipped out or switched places with someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:13.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or are you implying that I'm lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:14.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:15.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we don't suspect you of anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:20.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You believe you were with Mr. Oba through it all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:25.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,even while the murder was taking place...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:31.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a second, are you saying I helped him kill my father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:35.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I'm saying that the murder took place near you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:38.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's just that you didn't notice it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:42.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because at the time it happened, you had your
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.05,0:07:44.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,eyes closed & your back was to the elevator
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:46.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that's because you were kissing Mr. Oba...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:48.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were kissing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.29,0:07:51.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kissing... you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.73,0:07:52.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:58.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He cradled your head in his left arm like this, covering your ears and
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:03.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,while he was kissing you, he pushed the elevator call button
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.41,0:08:08.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And as soon as the door opened, your father was shot...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:10.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,by Mr. Oba...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:18.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But even if he covered her ears & used a silencer on the gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:21.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,wouldn't she have heard something when the body fell to the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:22.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:26.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe she would have heard a faint sound
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:32.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that's why Mr. Oba had the poppers go off just before the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:34.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he moved his arm away from her ears,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:36.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,just as the loud party poppers were going off,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.61,0:08:39.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the poppers would have made her forget about
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.34,0:08:44.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the faint sound she had heard previously...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.68,0:08:45.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:50.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he would have made sure the elevator door closed before he lowered his arm
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:51.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:54.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a very interesting story
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:59.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's one big hole in your theory,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:01.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tatsumi left because he wasn't feeling well
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.83,0:09:04.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,& he got into the elevator going down
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.20,0:09:07.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so why was he still inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:13.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You aren't saying that he was waiting inside for me to kill him, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.35,0:09:15.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's exactly what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:20.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he never left, he was waiting inside all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:24.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Waiting for you to come wearing your costume!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:29.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You probably told him something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:32.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Pretend you've gone home & change in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:34.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then you can return to the party & surprise everyone..."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.73,0:09:36.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.27,0:09:40.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what you're saying is, the victim's clothes were scattered because...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.87,0:09:45.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes... he was getting ready to change
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.51,0:09:46.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now I understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.68,0:09:51.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the elevator bell won't ring when the elevator's on hold...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:55.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On top of that, this is the company elevator...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.52,0:10:01.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Oba planned this knowing no one would use it until the party ended...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:04.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about the powder burns?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:07.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I was the killer, you would have found traces of it on me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:10.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand you winked
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:12.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I beg your pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:14.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of the girls told me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:18.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she said that while you were in the costume, you kept winking...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.64,0:10:20.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that made a light go off in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:23.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You weren't winking to make them laugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:26.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You hid something inside the eye
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:30.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that's why it wasn't working properly, isn't that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.79,0:10:33.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you already wore gloves on your right hand
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:37.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,& you put a plastic bag over the gun, closing it with rubber bands,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:41.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then you put it in the inside pocket of your jacket, making it portable
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:46.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and when the gun is fired, the powder wouldn't get onto your clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:50.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,& the empty casings wouldn't fall on the floor
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.81,0:10:54.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But she was close to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:57.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,wouldn't she have noticed him taking the gun out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.48,0:10:58.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:11:00.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it would have been obvious if things were like it is now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.52,0:11:02.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please turn off the lights
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:06.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,if the lights were dim like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.19,0:11:08.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the risk becomes far less...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:12.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and if he gives her a pendant, while they're here
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:15.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she'll lead him to the restroom where she'll put the pendant on
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:18.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,& then he can toss the gun down the dust chute near the rest room
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:20.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,without leaving her side
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:23.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Mr. Oba covered her ears & touched her earring,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.31,0:11:27.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,his left hand wasn't gloved...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.55,0:11:30.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that means, we should find some very nice prints
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:34.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,from your fingers on this plastic bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:40.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Humph, my fingerprints on the plastic bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.29,0:11:42.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course you'll find them...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:46.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,after all, I did touch that bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:50.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,along with the other people who helped me out of the costume!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:51.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:54.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wh, what does that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:56.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:57.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.01,0:12:01.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he's right, one of eyes wouldn't close so I opened it up & that bag was inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.88,0:12:04.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Oba said it might be some important part of the costume
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.15,0:12:06.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so we should leave it inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:07.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:10.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is my theory...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.49,0:12:13.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone who held a grudge against me, went down to the next floor
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:18.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,& shot Mr. Tatsumi while\NSakurako & I were at the restroom
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.16,0:12:22.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and then to frame me for it, the killer put that inside the costume...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.73,0:12:28.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it would have been easy since the costume was in the dressing room until I put it on,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:32.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think my theory sounds more realistic than your accusation
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:36.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that I shot him while engaged in a kiss is absolutely silly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:40.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kudo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:43.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well mister fresh out of school detective, do you have anything to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:47.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't seem so cocky now... what's the matter, run out of ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:51.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter, for every one of your questions
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:54.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a reasonable answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:15.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well mister fresh out of school detective, do you have anything to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.74,0:13:19.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't seem so cocky now...\NWhat's the matter, run out of ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.59,0:13:29.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pink pearl
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:33.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...Mr. Oba...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.23,0:13:39.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when you... gave her the pendant, you said this to her, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:44.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"It's a pink pearl pendant to go with the earrings you're wearing tonight"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.07,0:13:46.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, but what does that have to do with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.17,0:13:49.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:52.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did you know she had pink pearl earrings on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.34,0:13:53.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Humph...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.34,0:13:56.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,boy you're really grasping for straws aren't you... asking about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.08,0:13:58.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so obvious...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:09.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She told me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:12.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she bought those tonight on the spur of the moment
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:15.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,just before meeting you here tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:19.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,which means, you couldn't have seen them until you saw her here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:23.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And in this spot with the lights down so low,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:26.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,those pink pearls look like mere dark balls...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.91,0:14:31.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way you could tell they were pink...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.15,0:14:35.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right... not unless...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.55,0:14:40.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you opened this door of light
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:44.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,while you were kissing her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.36,0:14:49.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Oba... you couldn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:55.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, Mr. Oba, why don't you answer me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:59.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell us why you opened the door when you did...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.95,0:15:03.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you're asking me why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.85,0:15:06.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the answer is simple...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:09.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...Because I made a promise to my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:12.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that I would avenge his death...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.70,0:15:19.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Avenge your father's death?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.26,0:15:24.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes... my father also a rather big game company...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:27.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that was until 20 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:30.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when your father suggested their companies merge...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:36.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he suggested they open an office in the Beika Center Building...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:41.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he wasn't planning a merger, he was planning a take over...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:44.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,all the game creating know-how my father constructed, was stolen
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:49.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and all the employees in my father's company were laid off, one by one...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:51.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...and my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.33,0:15:56.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who was vice president in name only, was so full of despair, he killed himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:59.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But papa took such good care of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:06.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes... I think it was because he felt guilty, that's why he kept promoting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.61,0:16:08.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me, the man who planned to kill him,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:13.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,marry his daughter & take over the company!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.65,0:16:16.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th, that's so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:18.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was all a game...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:24.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the story line was, the hero uses the powers of evil to overthrow the demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.86,0:16:29.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but who would have thought it would end the same way...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:32.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:36.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father was murdered, but it was made to look like a suicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.04,0:16:41.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he was killed 20 years ago, right here in this very building by Mr. Tatsumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.21,0:16:44.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but someone saw through the crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:46.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it was a young man like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:49.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he figured it out just like you did tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:53.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess when you borrow the powers of evil, you have to pay the price...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.62,0:16:56.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's it! I remember it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.33,0:16:58.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was Yusaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:17:04.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yusaku Kudo butted in when we were investigating the case & he solved it for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:07.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're talking about that mystery writer...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.97,0:17:11.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means the son solved the crime which arose from the crime
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:15.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,committed 20 years ago which the father solved...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:19.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that ironic... don't you think, Kudo... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:21.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:31.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please... I need a little more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.70,0:17:35.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She... she's waiting for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:41.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't turn into Conan again now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.81,0:17:45.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ha, Haibara?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.78,0:17:47.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.45,0:17:49.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,why... why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.35,0:17:53.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,24 minutes over time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:56.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess that's the maximum tolerance level...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.35,0:17:58.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll consider this a loan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:03.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:07.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you hear?\NThe murder's been solved!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.26,0:18:08.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:11.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're finally going to get to see him, aren't you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:12.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See your boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:15.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For goodness sakes... he's not my boyfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.34,0:18:15.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:21.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Conan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:23.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, take this charge card!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.01,0:18:27.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi told me to give it to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:31.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle Kogoro told me to come check up on you & I ran into Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:33.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is dad here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.49,0:18:36.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes... he's waiting in the parking lot downstairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.29,0:18:39.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boy, what's taking that kid so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.56,0:18:41.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,1 whole hour's gone by already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:43.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't wait anymore,\NI'm going to go have a look myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.77,0:18:45.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I better just wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.74,0:18:47.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That wouldn't be adult of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.01,0:18:49.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rats...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.57,0:18:51.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So where is Shinichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.08,0:18:52.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.38,0:18:56.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's like this, he got a call on his cellular,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:57.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it was about a case he worked on recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:18:59.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,something terrible happened
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.98,0:19:02.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and so he ran off...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.29,0:19:04.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.26,0:19:11.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi's stupid, isn't he, leaving you all alone like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:14.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...So he left me behind again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.37,0:19:20.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...uh... you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.14,0:19:22.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi told me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:24.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:26.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:30.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...I don't want to hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.41,0:19:31.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,no more excuses...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.63,0:19:49.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...Shinichi told me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.34,0:19:54.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...one day
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.47,0:19:58.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,one day, for sure
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.04,0:20:04.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he'll come back, even if it kills him... that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:06.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:16.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wants you to wait for him... that's what he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.47,0:20:29.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...That's why... that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.18,0:20:32.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you're so silly Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.74,0:20:35.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you don't have to put on such a serious face...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:39.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all that eager beaver detective's fault,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.08,0:20:41.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he drops everything & runs off at the mere mention of a case!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.32,0:20:43.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eager beaver detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.32,0:20:47.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I almost forgot!\NConan, would you like some dessert?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.19,0:20:47.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.36,0:20:51.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, dessert menu please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.36,0:20:52.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.24,0:22:39.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of all the...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.80,0:22:43.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he has some nerve, asking me to wait for me, he says!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.01,0:22:46.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who does he think I am, his mother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.34,0:22:49.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th... that makes 5 desserts...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.98,0:22:54.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'd still like to know what he wanted to talk to me about...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.25,0:22:56.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan, aren't you curious too?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.05,0:22:59.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Uh... no, not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.92,0:23:05.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh well, since he ran off without telling me,\NI guess it wasn't very important...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.93,0:23:10.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just don't understand why he picked such an expensive restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.67,0:23:15.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a fool... making such a big deal when he had nothing important to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.27,0:23:19.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.71,0:23:30.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I picked this place for good luck
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.85,0:23:34.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,since dad proposed to mom here...
